
Setup Guide for United Sports Beacon

Welcome to United Sports Beacon! Follow this guide to set up your development environment.

---WIP---WIP---

Prerequisites
Ensure you have the following installed:
- Node.js (v16 or higher)
- npm (v8 or higher) or **yarn**
- Docker (optional, for containerized development)
- Git

---

Repository Structure
The repository is organized as follows:
- `backend/`: Contains backend microservices.
- `frontend/`: Contains web and mobile applications.
- `docs/`: Documentation for contributors and developers.

---

Setting Up the Development Environment

1. Clone the Repository
```bash
git clone https://github.com/TronDurell/United-sports-beacon.git
cd sports-beacon
